"{\n  \"text\": \"This is my cucumber garden. This is where we left off last week, and this is where I'm at now. The trellises are filling in very nice in the short expanses, they're all the way across. On the longer expanses, they're still getting there as you can see right here, but they'll be there shortly. This is a compost only garden. I'm not using any synthetic fertilizers. I'm using no herbicides or pesticides or anything of this nature because I'm trying to cultivate a living microbe-rich soil and plant. And so this fur this cucumber I'm trying to work off here is going to then get fermented where all those living microbes are going to get cultivated even further. And for those keeping up track at home, this is where we're at on the season. And like I said, I'm going to take all those microbes. I'm going to ferment them. This is some that just went in. Here's a progression shot of those ferments. So hold this thing on the left. Then I'm going to take all these uh wonderful cucumbers. I'm going to sell them at the farmers markets listed here in the Houston, Texas area, and I'll have tons of other stuff as well. Come out and see me and get some of this great stuff. See ya.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" This is my cucumber garden.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 1.68,\n      \"duration\": 1.44,\n      \"confidence\": 0.997,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" This\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" is\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" my\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" cu\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\"